    "summary": "The user is stuck at Heathrow after a flight cancellation and asks for practical travel advice to get to Singapore. The assistant responds by framing the entire situation through a goblin lens, providing a list of travel tips where every single point is heavily infused with goblin-themed metaphors and direct mentions of the creatures.",
